\c 62
\s Kunyarara kwomweya womunhu
\s anovimba naMwari
\s Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; nomutoo
\s waJedhutuni. Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 62 I Zvirokwazvo, mweya wangu
\s unongorindira Mwari;
\s Kwaari ndiko kunobva kuponeswa
\s kwangu.
\p
\v 2 Ndiye oga dombo rangu nomuponesi wangu;
\s Ndiye shongwe yangu yakakwirira; handingazununguswi zvikuru.
\p
\v 3 Muchavavarira munhu kusvikira riniko,
\s Kuti mumuuraye imi mose, Sorusvingo runoda kuwa, noruzhowa runotseyama?
\p
\v 4 Vanongorangana kuti vamusundire pasi abve paukuru hwake; Vanofarira nhema;
\s Vanoropafadza nomuromo wavo, asi vanotuka mumwoyo mavo.
\p
\v 5 Mweya wangu, rindira Mwari
\p zvirokwa
\v 7 NO;
\s Nokuti ndinomutarira iye.
\p
\v 6 Ndiye oga dombo rangu
\s noruponeso rwangu;
\s Ndiye shongwe yangu yakakwirira; handingazununguswi.
\p
\v 7 Kuna Mwari ndiko kunokuponeswa kwangu nokukudzwa kwangu; Dombo resimba rangu noutiziro hwangu zviri kuna Mwari.
\p
\v 8 Vimbai naye nguva dzose, imi vanhu;
\s Dururai mwoyo yenyu pamberi pake;
\s Mwari ndiye utiziro hwedu.
\p
\v 9 Zvirokwazvo vanhu vasingakudzwi mweya chete, uye vanhu vanokudzwa inhema;
\s Pakuyerwa havaremi;
\s Vose pamwechete vakareruka kupfuura mweya.
